## 📌 Project Overview

This project solves a real problem that many local businesses face:

- Their service is great — but their website doesn't say so
- Their value proposition is unclear
- Their calls-to-action are confusing
- Their content feels generic and outdated

**The solution:** Use AI prompt engineering to generate clear, benefit-driven, business-specific website copy that is ready to publish on a real website.

