## 💡 Why This Approach Works

Most local businesses lose customers not because their service is bad — but because their website fails to communicate their value clearly.

This project proves that with the right prompt engineering:

- A café in Boksburg can sound as compelling as any big city coffee brand
- Generic AI text can be avoided by being specific and local
- A complete, professional website can be produced in minutes
- The same prompt system can be reused for ANY local business

